┌─ INSTANT REJECTION CRITERIA ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                                                                                          │
│  ❌ TRUNCATION:       Content ends with "..." or incomplete sentences                   │
│  ❌ MULTIPLE CTAS:    "PRIMARY CTA OPTIONS:" or multiple call-to-action choices         │
│  ❌ SYSTEM ARTIFACTS: Development notes, database fields, technical content             │
│  ❌ FORMATTING:       Grammar errors, improper capitalization, missing punctuation     │
│                                                                                          │
│  ► IF ANY OF THESE ARE PRESENT: REJECT IMMEDIATELY AND REGENERATE ◄                    │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

┌─ 30-SECOND QUALITY CHECK ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                                                                                          │
│  1. SCAN FOR "..." ────── Instant rejection if found                                   │
│  2. COUNT CTAs ─────────── Must be exactly ONE call-to-action                          │
│  3. CHECK COMPLETENESS ── All sentences finished properly                              │
│  4. VERIFY VOICE ──────── Sounds like the business wrote it                            │
│  5. APPROVE/REJECT ────── No maybe - either perfect or regenerate                      │
│                                                                                          │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

┌─ PERFECT EXAMPLE (USE AS TEMPLATE) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                                                                                          │
│  Recovery is where champions are made! Everything athletes need to know about proper    │
│  recovery between training sessions and competitions. Ready to experience the           │
│  difference that professional recovery makes? Book your comprehensive recovery session  │
│  at Athlete Recovery Zone and discover how evidence-based recovery tools can transform │
│  your training and wellness journey. Contact us today to start your personalised       │
│  recovery experience.                                                                   │
│                                                                                          │
│  ✅ Complete content (no truncation)      ✅ Single, clear CTA                         │
│  ✅ Professional tone                     ✅ Business-branded call-to-action             │
│  ✅ Specific value proposition            ✅ Clean formatting                           │
│                                                                                          │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

