┌─ QUALITY STANDARDS CHECKLIST ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                                                                                          │
│  CONTENT COMPLETENESS:               BUSINESS VOICE MATCH:                              │
│  □ 40-60 words for short-form       □ Sounds like business wrote it                    │
│  □ Complete sentences only          □ Industry language appropriate                     │
│  □ No truncation anywhere           □ Brand personality reflected                       │
│  □ Professional formatting          □ Local references when appropriate                 │
│                                                                                          │
│  CALL-TO-ACTION QUALITY:            PROFESSIONAL STANDARDS:                             │
│  □ Single CTA only                  □ Grammar perfect                                   │
│  □ Specific action clear            □ Platform appropriate                              │
│  □ Business name included           □ Value clear to reader                             │
│  □ Contact method specified         □ Engaging hook present                             │
│                                                                                          │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

